Relationship manager 
- As a relationship manager, i want my special discounts rates to be displayed to me so that i can offer my clients competitive rates
- As a relationship manager, i want to choose from a range of potential vacations that suit the customer's preferences so that the customer can have the good time
- As a relationship manager, i want to know customer's details so that i can serve them with the best
- As a relationship manager, i want the up-to-date information displayed so that my clients can receive accurate information

- As a relationship manager, i want to be able to input customers payment details on there behalf, so that i can make a payment for a holiday package
- As a relationship manager, i want to be able to create, edit and delete my profile, so that i can keep customers updated on my skill, experiences and knowledge. 
- As a relationship manager, i want to retrieve customers details, so that i can make calls to outbound customers
- As a relationship manager, i want to view customers details and potential holiday packages, so that i can delivered a more specific and tailored service 
- As a relationship manager, i want to view a target list with all potential callers, so that i make calls with potential customers 
- As a relationship manager, i want to servce customers with the highest scores, so that i can achieve a sale efficiently 

Inbound customer 
- As an inbound customer, i want to be recognized by my number so that i can pay my travel with the payment method recorded in my user profile
- As an inbound customer, i want to view the travel packages in order of lowest to highest fares, so that i can choose the holiday packages efficiently.
- As an inbound customer, i want to connect to the RMs that serve me before so that i can work with them easily
- As an inbound customer, i want to save my favourite domestic destination so that i can choose it whenever i want

- As an inbound customer, i want to be directed to a relationship manager who is familliar with a particular holiday package, so that i can revieve reliable information about the place
- As an inbound customer, i want to view different holiday packages, so that i can develop more information about each place 
- As an inbound customer, i want to call a relationship manager, so that i can gather information about holiday packages 
- As a an inbound customer, i want to view the purchases made through the travel company, so i can review the holiday packages
- As an inbound customer, i want to view experiences and skills of relationship managers, so that i can develop more information of the places  and of the relationsip manager 

